{"tid":2422532,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★內房市場泡沫白熱化　業主為求甩手免費送樓","createTime":"2021-02-25T08:56:14.000Z","updateTime":"2021-02-25T10:23:00.000Z","uid":19454,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"1efc2c5e1c5615cde4e43324d4539bcd754c8dd4","tid":2422532,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:56:14.000Z","msg":"最近內地論壇上一則「送樓」貼文引發熱議，這名業主2016年購入河北省燕郊天洋城約40平方米尺的住宅單位，還剩下貸款70多萬人民幣未還清，發文「贈送天洋城房產，先到先得，自己還貸款」，希望將樓甩手<br />\n<br />\n不過，根據內地傳媒報道，業主表示並非失業破產，而是還貸壓力太大，且因工作要離開燕郊，之後沒機會住在這間樓。也就是說，這層樓並非完全免費贈送，承讓者仍須把剩下的貸款供完。但仍有不少評論認為，這是「棄樓斷供」案例！<br />\n<br />\n亦有當地代理指，還不起樓按貸款的情況不少，過去亦曾聞送樓例子，但承讓者通常佔不到便宜，因為這種樓大多高於市價，風險相對較高。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210225/bkn-20210225154347448-0225_00842_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Ffinance%2F20210225%2Fbkn-20210225154347448-0225_00842_001.html&d=L6ZqOc%2BI4Gry4yTyS7cXFdg1hcd%2FKl8HgBLPnoE2n08%3D&h=1c928ac0\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/finance/20210225/bkn-20210225154347448-0225_00842_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3bfb72e3fde5683d6c70993b951e930dc2997e45","tid":2422532,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T08:56:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0ab59b72687467815c0b8aa87900d90925516130","tid":2422532,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:00:07.000Z","msg":"之前唔係有單差唔多嘅咩?"},{"pid":"54080a26153c289afc344545c85068725a29eb9f","tid":2422532,"uid":53062,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-25T09:29:04.000Z","msg":"70多萬  